data.description: Embrace the warmth and charm of this beautiful red-brick home, nestled comfortably in a quiet cul-de-sac in Converse, Texas. The bright & welcoming interior offers an open-concept layout, with vaulted ceilings in the living room. The kitchen offers abundant storage space with beautiful two-tone cabinetry, granite countertops, and sleek modern fixtures.    Two of the three bedrooms feature ensuite bathrooms, creating aan opportunity for a perfect mother-in-law suite or a private home office.    Outside the expansive and fully fenced backyard features a cement patio, setting the stage for outdoor entertaining this fall!    The ideal location is 15 minutes from Randolph AFB, less than 10 minutes from multiple grocery stores (including Walmart and Sam's Club), and close to several schools and parks. Plus, living near 1604, you'll enjoy easy access to all the amenities you love in San Antonio!
